*   [named\_information (‚≠ê0)](https://github.com/spider-gazelle/named_information) - Naming Things with Hashes [rfc6920](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc6920)
*   [SPAKE2+ (‚≠ê2)](https://github.com/spider-gazelle/SPAKE2_plus) - Password Authenticated Key Exchange (PAKE) protocol, comparable to SRP-6a
*   [verhoeff (‚≠ê0)](https://github.com/spider-gazelle/verhoeff) - Implementation of the Verhoeff checksum algorithm
